description:
Root cause of rendering issue: #content-area div exists in index.html (line 90) wrapping address bar, new tab page, and webview container, but main.css has zero rules for it. Without display:flex and flex-direction:column, the entire main content area collapses instead of filling space between sidebars.

Fix: Add to main.css:
  #content-area { flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; position: relative; }
